# =============================================================================
# .gitignore for the P07 replication package.
#
# Philosophy: this study analyzes CONFIDENTIAL administrative data, so the rules
# below block anything that could carry restricted content by default, then ship
# only what is safe: the code, the documentation, and the disclosure-safe
# aggregate results. When in doubt, a file stays ignored.
#
# What IS shipped: scripts/, R/, the Quarto guide in book/, the aggregate result
# figures/tables in outputs/ and results/, the tidy aggregate layer in
# data/derived/, provenance/, manifest/, verification/, and the READMEs.
# What is NEVER shipped: any serialized data object (*.rds etc.), the restricted
# source inputs, provider coordinates, and secrets. See data/DATA_ACCESS.md.
# =============================================================================

# --- Serialized data objects: NEVER commit (defense in depth) ----------------
# The pipeline's inputs and intermediate objects are R/Arrow binaries that can
# carry provider-level or record-level content (e.g. the geocoded supply file,
# the raw 1,409 x 2,000 posterior draw matrix). None is shipped. The results
# that ARE shipped are CSV / GeoJSON / TeX / HTML / PDF / PNG, untouched by
# these rules.
*.rds
*.parquet
*.feather
*.dta
*.RData
*.rdata

# --- The data/ tree is protected --------------------------------------------
# Ignore everything under data/ EXCEPT the disclosure-safe aggregate layer
# (data/derived/, which holds only CSV/GeoJSON aggregates) and the READMEs.
data/**
!data/
!data/*.md
!data/derived/
!data/derived/**
# ...but even inside data/derived/, never admit a raw binary data format.
data/derived/**/*.parquet
data/derived/**/*.dta
data/derived/**/*.rdata

# --- Restricted source data: NEVER commit (see data/DATA_ACCESS.md) ----------
# The entire restricted-data/ tree is ignored except its README (the data
# contract). Obtain the DHR/Melissa/public source assets yourself and place
# them here (or point the environment variables at them); nothing here is ever
# distributed.
/restricted-data/*
!/restricted-data/README.md

# --- API keys / secrets: NEVER commit ----------------------------------------
*api_key*
*census_key*
.Renviron
.env

# --- R session / build artifacts ---------------------------------------------
.Rproj.user/
.Rhistory
.RData
.Ruserdata
.Rapp.history
*.Rcheck/
*.tar.gz
Rplots.pdf

# --- Quarto / rendered site artifacts ----------------------------------------
/book/_book/
/book/_freeze/
/book/.quarto/
.quarto/
/_book/

# --- OS / editor -------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*~
*.swp
